name: Emma Jane Maternity B-E Smooth Nursing Bra
description:
Maternity bra by Emma Jane
  • Smooth, soft handle cups

brand.name: Emma Jane
brand.description: Emma Jane creates maternity swimwear, lingerie and accessories with emphasis on great comfort and fit throughout your pregnancy. Soft nursing bras and maternity bras place focus on comfort and support alongside Emma Jane's collection of footless tights, super smooth opaques and one-piece swimsuits with lined finishes and hidden support accommodate your changing shape.

careInfo: Machine wash according to instructions on care label
